# Croncat journalism workflow dossiers (root-level JSON files only)
# Per-story JSON records (dossier + brief + post record) produced by the
# journalism pipeline. Contains copyrighted full article bodies — kept
# gitignored. The PUBLIC dossier viewer at docs/dossiers/ contains only
# metadata (no bodies) and IS committed.
/dossiers/

# Croncat journalism workflow drafts
# Dry-run draft posts land here as <story_id>_<post_type>.md. Local-only;
# the directory itself is tracked via a .gitkeep sentinel.
drafts/*
!drafts/.gitkeep
